These gorgeous Disney babes have many other responsibilities to attempt so they need your help to create an iconic look for the each member of the band. Join Princess Band Tees and be prepared to prepare the outfits that match their musical tastes! Their wardrobe is full of latest collection of must-have band tees. Mix and match as many as you can to create jaw-dropping looks in this brand new girls game!

Hope you would have great fun in this cool dress-up game with band theme! We cover many more popular titles from the category of princess dress up games for girls, no download required.
